reviewText: omg i love this dvd too funny if you like stand up your going to like this dvd ^_^ and it got to me on time
These episodes are hard to find as seasons but this is the best way to get them for now. funny as all get out.

I only bought this dvd for the Harland Williams portion and it was pretty disappointing.
BUT the dvd itself was in perfect condition.

I got two DVD's from Comedy Central, one would not paly at all on any of my DVD players and the other displayed the comics but was very poor picture quality. I will not buy any more products from Comedy Central. I did not return these Items, I do not have the time or the patients, so I will take my loss.
